         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395"><!-- p3l5-r11 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Hd1e108">Rubrica 11</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De vaniloquio et multiloquio</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e114">
               <lb ed="#V" n="33"/>
      ¶ De vaniloquio et multilo
      <lb ed="#V" n="34" break="no"/>quio Rubrica. 11
    </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e121">
               <lb ed="#V" n="35"/> <ref>SAlomon in prouerbiis.
      <lb ed="#V" n="36"/>c. 15.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e127">Respon
        <lb ed="#V" n="37" break="no"/>sio molis frangit iram: sermo du
        <lb ed="#V" n="38" break="no"/>rus suscitat furorem. Lingua pla
        <lb ed="#V" n="39" break="no"/>cabilis lignum vite.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e137"> 
             / <ref>16. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e139">Qui sapiens cor
        <lb ed="#V" n="40" break="no"/>de est appellabitur prudens: et qui dulcis elo
        <lb ed="#V" n="41" break="no"/>quio maiora percipiet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e148"> 
             / <ref>17. c.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e150">Cum obse
        <lb ed="#V" n="42" break="no"/>crationibus loquitur pauper: et diues effabi
        <lb ed="#V" n="43" break="no"/>tur rigide.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e158">
               <lb ed="#V" n="44"/>¶ <ref>Socrates in exhortationlbus. c. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e162">Esto
        <lb ed="#V" n="45"/>quidem modo suauis: verbo vero facetus. <!--193.xml-->
        <cb ed="#V" n="b"/>
                  <lb ed="#V" n="46"/>Est autem suauitas quidem salutare occurrem
        <lb ed="#V" n="47"/>tes. facetie vero alloqui eos lepidibus verbis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e176">
               <lb ed="#V" n="48"/>¶ <ref>Iesus filius sirach: in ecclesiast. c. 5.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e180">Pro
        <lb ed="#V" n="49" break="no"/>sequatur te verbum pacis et iustitie.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e186"> 
             / <ref>c. 6.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="50"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e188">Uerbum dulce multiplicat amicos: et miti
        <lb ed="#V" n="51" break="no"/>gat inimicos. Lingua gratiosa in bono ho
        <lb ed="#V" n="52" break="no"/>mine abundat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e198">
               <lb ed="#V" n="53"/>¶ <ref>Ouidius de arte amandi. lib. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e202">Asperitas
        <lb ed="#V" n="54"/>odium seuaque bella mouet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e208">
               <lb ed="#V" n="55"/>¶ <ref>Paulus apostolus epistola ad romanos.
        <lb ed="#V" n="56"/>c. 12.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e212">Benedicite: et nolite maledicere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e219">
               <lb ed="#V" n="57"/>¶ <ref>Cato. Capitulo. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e223">Saluta libenter. Blan
        <lb ed="#V" n="58" break="no"/>dus esto.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e229">
               <lb ed="#V" n="59"/>¶ <ref>Uersificator fabularum esopi. 38 fina.</ref>
        <lb ed="#V" n="60"/> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e233">Dulcia pro dulci pro turpi turpia reddi
        <lb ed="#V" n="61"/>Uerba solent: odium lingua fidemque parit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e241">
               <lb ed="#V" n="62"/>¶ <ref>Bernardus in l. de probatione viciorum
        <lb ed="#V" n="63"/>c. 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e245">Gratus vir: lingua cuique placere solet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e251">
               <lb ed="#V" n="64"/>¶ <ref>Henricus samariensis li. 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e255">Stillet in ore
        <lb ed="#V" n="65"/>fauus: sed mente resultet oliua.
        <lb ed="#V" n="66"/>Et non sit totus sensus in ore tuus.
        <lb ed="#V" n="67"/>Factaque si desint: non desint verba benigna.
        <lb ed="#V" n="68"/>Nam multos caros mellea lingua parit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e267">
               <lb ed="#V" n="69"/>¶ <ref>Gaufridus in poetria. c. 108.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e271">Mors et vi
        <lb ed="#V" n="70" break="no"/>ta coherent In manibus lingue.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-d1e277">
               <lb ed="#V" n="71"/>¶ <ref>Ricardus iudex venusinus l. de pertracta
        <lb ed="#V" n="72" break="no"/>tione nuptiarum. c. i.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d63395-Qd1e281">Pacem sermo bonus
        <lb ed="#V" n="73"/>gignit: et gaudia mestis
        <lb ed="#V" n="74"/>Cordibus infundit: tristitiamque leuat.
        <lb ed="#V" n="75"/>Ignis aqua: verbisque bonis extinguitur ira.
        <lb ed="#V" n="76"/>Sermo bonus quandoque magis quam facta porant.
        <lb ed="#V" n="77"/>Nil sermone bono gratius esse solet.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
